title: 118: What Did Your Dog Name You? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 118
description:
Rhett & Link are going back down the rabbit hole to discuss what dogs call their owners, pet ownership, and why Link is so okay with dog poop in the house on this week's Ear Biscuits.
